  "detailed_description": "<strong>Atomic Cards</strong> is an RPG card game in a post-apocalyptic world set where your money no longer has any value. A far more important goal is to obtain food, resources and weapons that will allow you to live a year in a new world devoid of morality and compassion. You will be faced with difficult life choices that affect how \"society\" will treat you. Will you be able to remain human in this hell reigning on Earth?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CREATE YOUR CHARACTER</strong><br>Choose a ready-made character with the characteristics that suit you or create your own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/dfd3ba453496dfb27e07aa051d0059d5.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/dfd3ba453496dfb27e07aa051d0059d5.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/dfd3ba453496dfb27e07aa051d0059d5.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>UNIQUE CARD COMBAT SYSTEM</strong><br>The use of weapons, armor, healing and perks is based on the principle of the card deck.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/5c27f8502113c8bcc5b946223bf7ab9f.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/5c27f8502113c8bcc5b946223bf7ab9f.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/5c27f8502113c8bcc5b946223bf7ab9f.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>CREATE A SHELTER</strong><br>To survive the cold nights of post-apocalypse<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/d65d1cb111e48250d1f3bb2b2c5716ba.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/d65d1cb111e48250d1f3bb2b2c5716ba.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/d65d1cb111e48250d1f3bb2b2c5716ba.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>EXPLORING THE WORLD</strong><br>Will reward you with various events.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/ab255c00d32ab91d5ac1030f450df2b5.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=596 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/ab255c00d32ab91d5ac1030f450df2b5.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/ab255c00d32ab91d5ac1030f450df2b5.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>PROCEDURAL WOLRD</strong><br>The generation of events, locations for exploration and events with a moral choice occur randomly with an accumulation of difficulty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/d5b4115b67ccfba6ee7c16a102061f5d.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/d5b4115b67ccfba6ee7c16a102061f5d.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/d5b4115b67ccfba6ee7c16a102061f5d.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>DARK ATMOSPHERE EXCITES YOUR MIND</strong><br>Every time you face a choice, you consciously follow the path of those moral values that you have chosen.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/0496dedaa196a1925e81450bcdef8dd0.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/0496dedaa196a1925e81450bcdef8dd0.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></li></ul><br>By playing Atomic Cards, you can show your worst sides and experience all the delights of the vicious world of post-apocalypse.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Atomic Cards</strong> is an RPG card game in a post-apocalyptic world set where your money no longer has any value. A far more important goal is to obtain food, resources and weapons that will allow you to live a year in a new world devoid of morality and compassion. You will be faced with difficult life choices that affect how \"society\" will treat you. Will you be able to remain human in this hell reigning on Earth?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>CREATE YOUR CHARACTER</strong><br>Choose a ready-made character with the characteristics that suit you or create your own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/dfd3ba453496dfb27e07aa051d0059d5.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/dfd3ba453496dfb27e07aa051d0059d5.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/dfd3ba453496dfb27e07aa051d0059d5.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>UNIQUE CARD COMBAT SYSTEM</strong><br>The use of weapons, armor, healing and perks is based on the principle of the card deck.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/5c27f8502113c8bcc5b946223bf7ab9f.poster.avif?t=1647960048\" width=320 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/5c27f8502113c8bcc5b946223bf7ab9f.webm?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701140/extras/5c27f8502113c8bcc5b946223bf7ab9f.mp4?t=1647960048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video><